overview.en: DiP (Divided Party) is a brand token listed on Ipparts Exchange (IPPAEX). The token is contractually backed by 48% of the Divided Party brand value. DiP raises funds for Federal Party SA - FPSA, a new political party in South Africa, and helps with the management of FPSA.
overview.zh: DiP (Divided Party) 是在 Ipparts Exchange (IPPAEX) 上市的品牌代币。该代币在合同上由 Divided Party 品牌价值的 48% 提供支持。 DiP 为南非新政党 Federal Party SA - FPSA 筹集资金，并帮助管理 FPSA.
